Titolo: Cosmonautica

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Cosmonautica is a video game that blends aspects of life simulation and space trading.  Players take control of a spaceship and crew it with characters, each of which has their own needs and skills.  By acquiring credits through missions, players can expand and customize their ship.  It was released via early access on PC in 2014, and the retail version was released in July 2015 on PC, Android, and iOS.

Genere: Life simulation game

Valutazione: 50
